Scotts Miracle-Gro Company - Wikipedia





















 






Scotts Miracle-Gro Company

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from The Scotts Miracle-Gro Company)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


The Scotts Miracle-Gro Company





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: SMG
S&P 400 Component


